	[em 
		"The Legend of Dragoon
	]em
	" is an RPG developed and published by Sony Computer Entertainment for the PlayStation in 1999. It follows the story of Dart, who swears to avenge the death of his parents by defeating a mysterious black monster. For reasons unknown, the Sandora Empire burns his native village down and arrest his childhood friend, Shana. Dart sets on a journey to rescue her; however, Shana's kidnapping sets off a sinister plot of ancient powers and the destruction of humanity.
